originalText.text:
I was appalled at the dismissive manner that you treated a black, male caller on your show on Thursday, October 27, 2022! Yes, he was rambling and incoherent. However, the way you chose to deal with it was by canceling him out in a most racist way. You totally disrespected him!
I texted my friends and shared the program with them. I was totally in awe of you up to that point! I've even recommended you to my friends. Now, I'm telling them about who you really are and providing proof!
